    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="header-title">这个“无需充电”的智能手表，人人都买得起！</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="article" id="contentMain">
        <div class="article-header">
            
            <p class="publish">
                <span class="team">创次方</span>
                <span class="author">菱角</span>
                <span class="data">昨天08:00</span>
            </p>
        </div>

       <div class="content clearfix" id="articleContent">
           
               <div class="rich_media_content " id="js_content">
<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">苹果手表确实不错，但价格土豪且不说，这一天一充实在不能忍。。。 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><img data-="" data-ratio="0.5541284403669725" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="545" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/oxSkMz_Ab5kGFfmPYK460eTElDkuoYt50rF4F0thNvMhAgAALgEAAEpQ.jpg" style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">今天隆重推出无需充电的智能手表 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> <strong> STARK </strong> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ，低调奢华，人人都买得起！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.6661764705882353" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="680" src="http://2.im.guokr.com/vNroxWxldJ9L2UWuDypL1kTjfwuelJws-20P3ucu-mCoAgAAxQEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">你能想到的智能手表功能， </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 几乎全都具备，而且兼容&nbsp;iOS 与安卓平台！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="" src="http://2.im.guokr.com/evT0F3gzqBqy195FjrSwhELFPRd7pTjMch2Jv71PEHD-BQAAYQMAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">收到 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 短信和 APP 信息 </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ， <strong> STARK </strong> 表盘下方 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 指示灯闪烁 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ✨，并伴随有清晰的 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 提示音 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.5549525101763908" data-type="gif" data-w="737" src="http://3.im.guokr.com/ejBsUDzkHJhJ3KfO53VvLtqSuXwXrue4F9Djcw-qHiDhAgAAmQEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">拉近一点看。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.563169164882227" data-type="gif" data-w="467" src="http://3.im.guokr.com/dnlUPMd68F-QyN9GKx0pLTGYoksWRW1W_sPs9N2OzarTAQAABwEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"><strong>来电提醒 </strong> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ，再也不错过楼下快递小哥的电话了！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/QYWbGVvF7CI0jpHgm-AAeR9uQ5ogWq54XqdXDo8RFJ0AAgAAIAEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">睡前设好 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> <strong> 闹钟 </strong> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ，早上 <strong> STARK </strong> 定时叫你醒。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="608" src="http://2.im.guokr.com/7wa724B6rCSjTj-cjUfHQD7IP1x8cWtIigOtRf2fsupgAgAAVgEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 还与苹果 HEALTH 连接，对晚上的各种 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> <strong> 睡眠数据 </strong> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 进行跟踪。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/3HBzVrnz_tqeVCWl7m6iEL941UG0qxnh_RhiuSOUuteAAgAAaAEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"><strong>运动追踪 </strong> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 功能当然也必不可少！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/ej-BmX7X5xlAx3kh4unQqEcZ4yAfqiQSNoaafIVJmCbAAQAA_AAAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">设置目标，计步、距离、路线、锻炼和卡路里消耗都可以有！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/TCgzklynlqS0JsluFZw73Btj7m2ZJXEqJu1dayyEqh2AAgAAaAEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">各种数据都能通过 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 短信、邮件或社交平台 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 进行分享！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.5645695364238411" data-type="gif" data-w="604" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/C3njQHnTwfY_ftaCmfLoMoEyzb0nsHPORO_uJ4BC0SFcAgAAVQEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">出门忘记了带 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ，手机和手表同时响起，很快找到手表。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.5625" data-type="gif" data-w="544" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/Bv3J0XTwJPwMxzarU4HJiDs7THWMURziRilyX04BjCQgAgAAMgEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">此外，还可以通过甩一甩 </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 远程操控手机拍照 </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ！</span></p>

<p><span>如果不需要闪灯和声音提示，配备的 APP 即可关闭。</span></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">硬件方面， <strong> STARK </strong> 最大卖点是 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 不用充电 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ！</span></p>

<p><strong><span>STARK </span> </strong> <span> 内部包含两大模块： </span> <span> 运动模块 </span> <span> 和 </span> <span> 智能模块 </span> <span> ，各有一块电池供电。</span></p>

<p><span>运动模块 </span> <span> 是&nbsp;EPSON AL20， </span> <span> 用于支持指针行走 </span> <span> ，采用 </span> <span> VINNIV（松柏） L626 </span> <span> 电池，可用 <strong> 2 </strong> 年！！</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/xKJo-iNfI9guqlqp1c_BPUu7EqMvVMsQw7M4s4VPbQRtAgAAXQEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span>（指针运动模块）</span></p>

<p><span>智能模块 </span> <span> 通过蓝牙 <strong> 4.0 </strong> 与手机连接， </span> <span> 进行数据传输 </span> <span> ，电池型号是 </span> <span> CR 2032 </span> <span> ，可供 <strong> 4-7 </strong> 个月正常使用，贴心的团队再附赠一个备用电池。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-type="gif" data-w="" src="http://1.im.guokr.com/li4drym6dvoSz9gfM2gyi1df8h6W4WAwUJI4Cu5mStSAAgAAaAEAAEdJ.gif"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">这两种电池都可以在某宝上容易买到，团队还附赠了小工具刀，轻松自行更换。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.7741312741312741" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="518" src="http://2.im.guokr.com/n7ekS1PcLKvOQ3sK0uHKAr-_6zl5Sk4qC728wVJ4kn4GAgAAkQEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 构造实用简单，拒绝浮夸路线。</span></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">表壳采用耐操耐磨 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 不锈钢 </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> </span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> ，直径 <strong> 42 </strong> 毫米，厚度 <strong> 11 </strong> 毫米。</span></p>

<p><span>表带材质为 </span> <span> 热塑性聚氨酯 </span> <span> ，最大/最小长度为 <strong> 21 </strong> 厘米/ <strong> 15.5 </strong> 厘米，宽度 <strong> 22 </strong> 毫米。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="" src="http://3.im.guokr.com/UzgO0FC_KZcRf7Xs2FIJgArCpDAkvhZrAg6LGcicMH2oAgAAxQEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">表镜采用蓝膜玻璃，直径 </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 22 </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 毫米，硬度 5.5（相当于不锈钢的硬度）。</span></p>

<p><span>两根表针夜晚荧光。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.425" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="680" src="http://3.im.guokr.com/ZTk4r8N6jnbtTyYzy2RBqKJjfGq7Dn07GjTXuI17dEeoAgAAIQEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">防水深度达 </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 30 </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 米。</span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0.6826003824091779" data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-w="523" src="http://3.im.guokr.com/QHVtmw6MZaXGig-KNDUuT-oigaQ3es-laS0gJ_zsuC4LAgAAZQEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

<p><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;">说到口吐白沫，你却只想问我 </span><strong style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> STARK </strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.06em;"> 智能手表究竟有多便宜？</span></p>

<p><span><strong>STARK </strong> 超级早鸟价&nbsp;$ <strong> 4 </strong> <strong> 0 </strong> ，买不了吃亏，买不了上当。 </span></p>

<p><img data-="" data-ratio="0" data-s="300,640" data-type="png" data-w="" src="http://2.im.guokr.com/l5vWy4H8PbadlAUsD_m9mqR8OYIvDzHGes10lffkH3FEAwAAmwEAAEpQ.jpg"></p>

